    <body>
        <header>
            <h1>Justin Martz</h1>
            <h2>Full-stack Java Developer</h2>
        </header>

        <nav id="nav-bar">
            <ul>
                <li><a class="link-button active" href="#about" >About</a></li>
                <li><a class="link-button" href="#projects" >Projects</a></li>
                <li><a class="link-button" href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                <li><a class="link-button" href="#resume">Resume</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>

        <main>
            <article id="articles">
                <div class="sections about-container" id="about">
                    <div class="about-container">
                        <div class="about-text">
                            <p>For the lack of a better word I call them hangy downs. Let that brush dance around there and play. All you have to learn here is how to have fun. Even the worst thing we can do here is good. This is your world. You can bend rivers. But when I get home, the only thing I have power over is the garbage.</p>
                            <br>
                            <p>The only thing worse than yellow snow is green snow. By now you should be quite happy about what's happening here. Let's have a little bit of fun today.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="about-picture">
                            <img src="images/photo.jpg" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="galleria">
                        <img src="photo1.jpg">
                        <img src="photo2.jpg">
                        <img src="photo3.jpg">
                    </div>
                </div>
            
            <div class="sections" id="projects">
                <div class="projects-container">
                    <div class="project">
                        <img src="images/housefire.jpg">
                        <h1>Urban Wildfire Simulator</h1>
                        <p>Enter your location, set the weather conditions, and analyze the aftermath!</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project">
                        <img src="images/man.jpg">
                        <h1>Election 2024</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project">
                        <img src="images/scale.jpg">
                        <h1>Scale Buddy</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project">
                        <img src="images/therapy.jpg">
                        <h1>Therapy HQ</h1>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="sections" id="contact">
                <h1>Contact page</h1>
                <p>I get carried away with this brush cleaning. This is probably the greatest thing to happen in my life - to be able to share this with you. Nothing's gonna make your husband or wife madder than coming home and having a snow-covered dinner. You have to make these big decisions. Maybe there's a happy little bush that lives right there.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="sections" id="resume" style="display: none">
                <h1>resume page</h1>
                <p>Get away from those little Christmas tree things we used to make in school. There's nothing wrong with having a tree as a friend. I sincerely wish for you every possible joy life could bring.

                    There is no right or wrong - as long as it makes you happy and doesn't hurt anyone. Let your heart be your guide. Trees get lonely too, so we'll give him a little friend.</p>
            </div>
        </article>
    </main>
        
